name: D i v ! n g H i g h
description: I drew this one looking at the street with my housemate. We listened to nostalgic songs and remembered one I liked a lot. She said it sounded like a 2001 soundtrack. It's my favorite book. I really wanted to go into the unknown in the solar system in search of something that I still don't know exactly what it is. You know... being able to say “it's just that they called me earlier and said I need to go” / 2020
